# SharePoint integration is LOCAL-only per the SP NO-PUSH policy. Canonical
# source lives at /opt/ahg-sp-integration/ on the integration host; the
# Heratio-side port in app/Domain/SharePoint/ must NEVER be committed.
/app/Domain/SharePoint/
